   NOTICE TO OUR VISITORS:
   The information provided herein to our visitors is intended to provide
   Section 508 information and guidance. The Section 508 personnel
   providing this information to you cannot speak with authority for your
   particular agency, and as such, the Section 508 website is provided as
   a resource for general guidance only. The answers provided via our Q&A
   section from 508 Technical or 508 Procurement mailboxes, do not bind
   the government, and may not be relied upon for litigation or other
   purposes.

